---
import { SITE } from '@/config/site';
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-[1280px] mx-auto overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:8c142p">
  
  <!-- Header Title -->
  <div class="text-center mb-16 hero-animate" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:7c332k">
    <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-dark tracking-tight mb-6" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:mc3sh9">About <span class="text-primary" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:1x6f7k">SPVH Group</span></h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-screen-xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:xmf8iw">We are a Indian origin asset management firm driven by an operator-investor mindset. By strategically allocating capital to best-in-class operators and businesses, we engineer diversified portfolios designed to compound wealth and deliver enduring impact across geographies.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 1: Founder Profile -->
  <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg mx-auto mb-32 hero-animate-delay-1 group" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:p8v49">
    <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-dark/5" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:x9v92">
      <img
        src="/images/Sujay-1024.webp"
        alt="Sujay Prakash - Founder of SPVH Group"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out"
        loading="eager"
      data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:k4m38"/>
      
      <!-- Gradient overlay for text readability -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark/80 via-dark/20 to-transparent opacity-60" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:m9k12"></div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Glassmorphism Name Badge (Pop-out effect) -->
    <div class="absolute -bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[90%] md:w-[110%] p-6 md:p-8 rounded-[1.5rem] bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-2xl shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] border border-white/50 z-10 text-center transition-all hover-lift" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:n2b38">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-2 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:lv25cc"><strong class="font-extrabold text-primary">Sujay Prakash</strong></h2>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-[3px] text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:xmf8ix">Promoter and UBO</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 2: A Message from Our Founder -->
  <div class="relative w-full max-w-[1280px] mx-auto rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white px-8 md:px-16 py-12 shadow-xl border border-border/50 reveal-scale" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:c9v27">

    <!-- Decorative Quote Mark -->
    <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-6 md:-left-12 text-[120px] md:text-[160px] leading-none text-primary/10 font-serif font-black select-none pointer-events-none" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:q2p19">
      "
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-dark mb-10 text-center relative z-10 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:le0i7f">A Message from Our Founder</h3>

    <div class="prose prose-lg md:prose-xl prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-p:text-dark-muted/90 text-justify max-w-none relative z-10 space-y-6" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:w3m92">
      <p data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:xmf8iy">SPVH Group was founded with a clear belief — capital, when guided with discipline, vision, and responsibility, has the power to create long-term value beyond financial returns. Our focus has always been on building an institution that combines strategic thinking, prudent risk management, and deep market understanding to serve Institutional and Ultra High Net Worth clients across evolving market cycles.</p>

      <p data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:ade3j6">At SPVH, we view asset management not merely as the allocation of capital, but as the responsibility of aligning opportunity with purpose. Through a multi-asset and research-driven approach, we aim to create sustainable growth while maintaining the highest standards of governance, transparency, and client alignment.</p>

      <p data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:ade3j1">We thank our clients, partners, and stakeholders for their continued trust and confidence as we continue this journey together.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Closing -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-border/50 col-span-full" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:h8k31">
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-2" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:ade3j0">Warm regards,</p>
      <img src="/images/SP-Fancy-Sign-2-768.webp" alt="Sujay Prakash Signature" class="w-56 max-w-full h-auto -mb-6 relative z-0 object-contain rotate-20" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:nuj3r3" />
      <div class="text-2xl text-dark relative z-10 mt-4" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:t3b29">
        <strong class="font-extrabold text-primary block mb-1">Sujay Prakash</strong>
        <span class="block text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-2" data-ps="src/components/about/Founder.astro:1x6f7j">Promoter and UBO</span>
        <strong class="font-bold text-dark tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">SPVH Group</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
